                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-68-defend677 t18060219-68-punish380"></join>
               Confined Six Months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18060219-68-punish381" type="punishmentDescription">
