                     <interp inst="t18060219-68-punish381" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-68-defend677 t18060219-68-punish381"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
